entries.title_d: Your acts of piracy have gained the attention of the CorSec. They cannot be allowed to report in to your actions. Destroy them all.
entries.title: Space Corellia: Destroy the CorSec Fighters
entries.split_quest_alert: There will be no witnesses to your actions. Travel to the Tatooine system, inspect, and pickup the brandy for the Lord's Mistress.
